</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=xalmatelemental>XalmatElemental</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 63<br> <font color=#333333>(2/26/03 8:51:55 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm29.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1016.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Pets and Shields</span><hr size=1> Why do you want to give your pet a shield? The extra AC does not make up for losing half of your pet's offensive ability. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :rolleyes --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/eyes.gif ALT=":rolleyes"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=nimmamen>Nimmamen</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 82<br> <font color=#333333>(2/26/03 10:30:41 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm29.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1016.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Pets and Shields</span><hr size=1> shields were always very useful up to 24.. and i used shields up to 33 because the extra bash damage actally outweighed the small chance of a 2x wield. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=shanukdandiprat>ShanukDandiprat</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 62<br> <font color=#333333>(2/26/03 10:41:06 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm29.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1016.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Pets and Shields</span><hr size=1> <br>
