 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=rhasinfirestorm@themagicianstower>Rhasin Firestorm</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Sage</span><br>  Posts: 1326<br> <font color=#333333>(2/26/03 10:54:51 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm29.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1016.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Pets and Shields</span><hr size=1> There is an alternative to pets autoequipping the shield in the back slot, in that he's not wearing it at all. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://&quot;http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=52886&quot;"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://home.attbi.com/~c.wroten/graphics/Rhasin_sig.jpg" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=shanukdandiprat>ShanukDandiprat</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 63<br> <font color=#333333>(2/26/03 11:32:14 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm29.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1016.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Pets and Shields</span><hr size=1> <br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr><br>
If you want to further test this try giving a naked pet a dropped shield that is secondary only. If he equips it, my theory is correct. If not, maybe he just ignores the shield as it would hamper his ability to dish out damage :-) <br>
<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
